      "title": "VTA to host Annual Twusuper Golf Day",
      "country": "AU",
      "crawl_date": "2017-10-24T05:08:23Z",
      "url": "http://www.primemovermag.com.au/news/article/vta-to-host-annual-twusuper-golf-day",
      "host": "primemovermag.com.au",
      "text": "VTA to host Annual Twusuper Golf Day   \nThe Victorian Transport Association (VTA) has said that it is well on-track to break previous record attendance for the Annual Twusuper Golf Day to be held 13 November at Commonwealth Golf Club in Melbourne. \nThe VTA has confirmed it can still accommodate additional teams and individual players to what is one of the transport industry’s most popular golf days. \n“We’d love to have more new faces attend this enjoyable event, which is a great opportunity to play on one of Melbourne’s most challenging golf courses and network and do business with other transport industry representatives,” said VTA CEO, Peter Anderson. \n“Commonwealth Golf Club is regarded by golfing enthusiasts as one of the finest in the country and we are pleased that the Twusuper Golf Day is able to return to Commonwealth for the third consecutive year. \n“Located in the Melbourne Sandbelt, the stunning course has hosted the Australian Open, Women's Australian Open and Victorian Open, and is the perfect setting for this fantastic event,” he said. Featured Article",
